  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an open-label phase 1-b study to evaluate the safety and efficacy of CCX872-B in
      patients with pancreatic adenocarcinoma also receiving FOLFIRINOX chemotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
